snippet.title: Black Book - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: A fusion of card-based RPGs and Adventure games, “Black Book” is a haunting tale of a young sorceress, who gave her life to serve the dark forces.  Add to Steam wishlist: https://bit.ly/39WlruS
